snippet: Stopped by for an anniversary dinner after the Jays game. Service was great, food was great, and even got a card and complimentary desert for our anniversary! 5 star experience!

name: Ru Selvadurai
snippet: A great location with extremely helpful staff. If asking for something for takeaway for a friend or yourself make sure it's not a starter as their containers are made for steaks and veggies.. The food will look/feel unappetizing in those.

name: Victor
snippet: Of the handful of The Keg franchise locations in Toronto, this one is near the top of the list. The service is consistently great, and the food is always fantastic. This location does not take reservations, so plan ahead!

name: Krista Galivan
snippet: Always the best service and food. It was my birthday and I was surprised with a delicious dessert and hand written card. Very thoughtful team!

name: Felipe Soares
snippet: Love this location! We absolutely love Nicole. Amazing server, very friendly and just the best 💕

name: John Vlahakis
snippet: Consistent food as always however social distancing within the restaurant is non existent, tables regular distance

name: a McTaggart
snippet: This place is huge! The food was good and so was there service. We went for a birthday dinner on a busy night and the amount of people made it difficult to maintain a conversation with the people at our table.

name: Jamie G
snippet: The Keg always lives up to expectations and continually against trendy steak restaurants charging exorbitant prices. This location is no exception. Great service. The escargot, blue cheese filet mignon...divine.

name: Mac
snippet: Went to the Keg for the first time and had a wonderful experience! Came with a giftcard and our server Elizabeth was quick, super friendly and wonderful, defintely plan on coming back again for a great time and amazing cocktails!

name: Jennifer P. Chung
snippet: Never had a bad meal here. I go about once a month as a little treat for myself 14oz prime with grilled shrimp. Always good :) and the staff are always wonderful.

name: Munish Sharma
snippet: Dinner and a Show! Couple glasses of J.Lohr and Crème brûlée plus and exciting medival times brawl at the bar. Glass in the leg@thekeg. Def recommend for first date!

name: Davis Wu
snippet: Steak was cooked and seasoned perfectly.

name: Eirina Grennan
snippet: Amazing dinner and service! Didn't have to tell them it was my birthday. They asked if we celebrating and then gave us a huge piece of icecream cake at the end.

name: William G. Lozza
snippet: Excellent place for dining in the heart of the city, beautiful patio, delicious food, staff is nice and friendly. A pleasure to visit.

name: Daniel Clark
snippet: Kayla was amazing and took great care of us on our 2nd day in Canada. The food was epic, a definite must for all food lovers. Great atmosphere too. Thank you all x

name: Nancy Hughes
snippet: Lindsay at the bar made my pre-birthday extra special surprising me with a cake!! So friendly here! They care about people. We came for their amazing margaritas and those delectible little neptunes ( crab stuffed mushrooms). The prime sliders rocked. And ooo the cake!! Happy birthday girll! 😊Everything came to us super fast. Perfect evening!!

name: Sébastien St-François
snippet: Excellent service and free dessert to celebrate our first wedding anniversary. Nicely appreciated!

name: Jacquie Kelly
snippet: Great food with amazing staff make this a great night out for dinner! Still out fav place in Downtown TO for steak!

name: Oliver Dempsey
snippet: Great food , great service very nicely laid out inside. Washrooms are clean This is certainly one of the better Keg restaurants Some of the chairs in the upper lounge are a little low and hard to sit and eat from would be my only reason for not giving 5 stars

name: Mohammed Shaheen
snippet: Man.. the Keg literally turning into MacDonald for steaks.. nothing special about anything there. Even the presentation, the service.. Everything is so generic and brutal boring there . The food itslef.. just like a steak at jack Astor or any diner.. Anyway.. guess it's the only way to make quick fast money..

name: Vivian leung
snippet: Great food and good atmosphere. Staff very friendly.

name: COVERT CRUZER HD
snippet: The service and food at this location was excellent for a birthday event on January 30th, 2020, however my review on here is addressed with how poor the customer cellar network "HSPA" speeds were while dinning inside... Let me tell you, it was dreadfully slow, I am talking about 4G speeds, to the point where my web browsing experience was not even loading anything at all... In the downtown core of T.O, this not acceptable for 2020. But then again, the structure of the building has something to do with the poor signals. On the other hand, the Kegs wifi network was also pretty slow as well but somewhat acceptable, about 5Mbp/s download speeds... Let's see what Roger's 5G network will bring to the table later in this year.

name: Banu Bayram
snippet: Went here for my boyfriends surprise dinner and the service was great. Accommodated all of my requests for the private room called the library. Great night!

name: Seuth Bouttarath
snippet: It's the Keg. Consistency is expected and most times delivered. That night I went, they served up solid drinks, and the staff was very friendly. Easy to recommend.

name: Graeme Neil
snippet: Bartender served me very tasty drink while I was waiting for my dinner partner to come. Dinner was excellent as well. Great location to boot.

name: CC LARA
snippet: Great service and reasonable prices. Drinks were not watered down, steaks and prime ribs cooked perfectly but mushrooms side way too salty

name: C Winston
snippet: Great food great service love the ambiance.

name: G Kim (watunid)
snippet: Great dinner with kind staffs Delicious and satisfied seasoned steaks menus with reasonable price Really enjoyed the dinner time with my coworkers Hope to visit again :D

name: Izzy
snippet: This is a great location. Super nice staff; great food; great experience.

name: Tim Jankov
snippet: The steaks were amazing, but one of our steaks was slightly undercooked. They brought it back promptly with new sides. Great atmosphere and drinks too

name: M K
snippet: Great location for the keg right on King W. The food was great, service was good. I've gone with small and large groups.

name: Mike Williams
snippet: Great location. I have been to all but one of the locations in the GTA and the king st location is the best. The service is great and the food is exactly as expected. Well done.

name: Renee Williams
snippet: Great service and great food!

name: Frances Ariganello
snippet: Everything was fantastic from the time we went inside until the time we left. The service was the best ever the food was fantastic cooked to perfection.The place was pretty full. Thankyou for a wonderful meal.

name: Yen love
snippet: The food is very delicious.. The only thing I didn't like is when the hostess ask us if we are going to leave soon and mentioned our longer stay...I went with my cousin who is visiting from states as you can imagine we had a lot to catch up ...so we stay for 2.5 hours having dinner and drinks...we paid the bill earlier because we were waiting for someone to pick us up....anyways I feel like overstayed when asked if we are leaving...!!!

name: Steve Smith
snippet: Consistently good. Took my daughter for her birthday and they offered a complimentary glass of champagne. First time I've seen a Keg do that. Nice touch!

name: kath reyes-cordero
snippet: Amazing food and excellent service

name: Ronan Frawley
snippet: The Keg is a model franchise of consistency. Great steak, wine and atmosphere. What makes this location stand out from the rest are the staff. Great people!

name: Carim “Cas London” James
snippet: The keg on King is a mansion sized building and offers a fantastic blend of upper class eating experience within an affordable budget, albeit a special occasion restaurant, it offers high quality and great service.

name: Neil Stevens
snippet: Dropped in for late night appies and drinks. Great service and food as always!!!

name: David Gluzman
snippet: Always take thr burger. Great deal and super good. The service was not so much that day but thats just one waitress amongst many that served me at this location.

name: Ryan Forsyth
snippet: First time at The Keg and it was amazing! I was accompanied by one other person and we were told the wait is an average of 1:30min. In reality, we waited 20 min before getting seated.

name: Robert K
snippet: Lunch was delicious. Staff were professional. Seating was well spaced out. A good time was had by all.

name: Joshua Alexander
snippet: I am not the big fan of KEGs. Have few unhappy memories from other locations. But this location is almost perfect. Good service and excellent steak.

name: natasha “NR” robinson
snippet: Awesome Service! Management helped me celebrate nephew's new job! Great server great food....fast service great experience from beginning to end!

name: Alejandro Martínez
snippet: Excellent service, after all this time of lockdown is good to be back! Great food!

name: Batmath
snippet: I had tge ribs, they were pretty good .The fries were sublime and my girlfriend had a steak wish was perfectly cooked.

name: TC
snippet: As good as it gets. Service was unreal. Went for a Bach they were super accommodating. Food came out perfect and wines were great.

name: Karim Al-Mradi
snippet: 30$ for a dry bland chicken leg and a couple cute kiddie sized vegetables. My pina colada was way to sweet. Embarrassing

name: Tina Hurley
snippet: Awesome service and food. We Will be back very soon.

name: José Dávila
snippet: My first time at a The Keg Restaurant. Great food! Although, the service can improve a little bit more.

name: V Ladeira
snippet: Cant get disappointed. I had a special with shrimp, lobster, steak and warm corn and feta salad. Amazing!!

name: Eric L
snippet: This King St location lacks some of the charm of their other properties, but still serves the hearty food and drinks you expect from the Keg. Prices are reasonable for the type and segment of restaurant, but it isn't quite at the level of their admittedly pricier competitors.

name: T D.S
snippet: Great service , Luke our server was knowledgeable about the menu , very likable. Food was fresh and came out on time.

name: Let's go Walking
snippet: Out of all the Kegs this one is my favorite. Service is always wonderful. I always order my steak blue and out of all the Kegs that Ive been too, this is the only one that gets it close.

name: Fred Nicholson
snippet: Closest location to our house. We liked the feel and service of this restaurant. The food was delicious and a great experience. Highly recommended.

name: John Roman
snippet: Great ambiance, first time going to one. Steak was slightly undercooked and serving size was on the small side.

name: Kolt Curry
snippet: Great takeout probably the only time did steak takeout ND the keg on king didn't disappoint

name: Peter Galindo
snippet: Courteous hosts, excellent (and polite) service, the dining room is incredible, the food is even better. There is plenty of variety on the menu, too, which is nice.

name: Louise Rogers
snippet: Fantastic steak! Very nice ambiance. Not too loud. Thoroughly enjoyed our dinner and evening!

name: Jeff Uren
snippet: One of the newest Keg locations. Great atmosphere and the steaks are always well prepared. Quite a decent wine list.

name: J T
snippet: The Keg...the expensive McDonald's for the wealthy. Poor service, industrial type fries (really the Keg? You can't cook fresh fries?) And average steak.Make sure you bring a lantern if you want to see what you are eating.

name: Yakuza Blade
snippet: Great atmosphere as well as walk ins for in case you didn’t book a reservation. Nothing is guaranteed, but service and food are of the highest quality

name: Giordano Manuel
snippet: Excellent service, great management and amazing food! Love to sit on the patio in the summer. The interior is also very beautiful.

name: Malik Chabou
snippet: Good food, good drinks - but too busy to seat anyone quickly. Come 30 minutes early and be prepared to wait.

name: Nicco Tancredi
snippet: Such a beautiful modern interior, for a great romantic dinning experience ! Its not a cheap dinner, but makes for a great special occasions place.

name: Carissa McCabe
snippet: Very good food with the right price. Downside is the portions being a little too much. Will come again though.

name: Peter Arth
snippet: Great location, popular area. Food is good, what you'd expect from the Keg. Parking is available underground in the building, entry off of King Street, next to condo.

name: Joy Durance
snippet: My Dad and mom went and both got sick same meal and same symptoms afterward .

name: Sherif Heleka
snippet: Excellent service and delicious food. We were a party of 15 and the staff was very accommodating.

name: Alejandro Calderon
snippet: Always a great location for “happy hour” and/or watch a game. There should be bigger TV screens and or more in the bar and bar-lounge area.

name: Jeff S Brodie
snippet: Great ambiance. We were a group of 10 and we had a great meal, great service, and a good wine selection.

name: Jenn Helder
snippet: Just had a lovely date night. Tori was amazing. Please thank her for her friendly service! Her hard work was appreciated:)

name: Claire Woods
snippet: Food is always good, it’s the keg after all. Service is declining, but I’ll still come back for the steak

name: Jeff V
snippet: Always a great experience. The steak is amazing, the service is always great and it's a perfect bang for your buck ratio.

name: Yasir Azhar
snippet: Great service and atmosphere plus the food was perfect as always.

name: Loris T
snippet: Had a wonderful dinner there last week. Great food and waiter was very pleasant.

name: pl87
snippet: Great service. Good food. What you expect from a steak chain: high price, standard steak meal.

name: Robert O'Connell
snippet: Nice menu...and there's even a non salad vegetarian option too! Would like to see more vegetarian choice though.

name: Laurice Day
snippet: Accommodating staff, nice patio. Great for business meetings. Good steaks, as usual.

name: Ana Maric
snippet: The food is amazing, the ambience is almost perfect on this world the service is absolutely perfect and the steak is what you look always for ....the best softy one 😋💪

name: Mark
snippet: Great service, everything was super smooth. Had a great evening.

name: Wayne Curtis
snippet: Great service. Great food. Good value.

name: Phil W
snippet: We didn't have food here but had some drinks I must say the place was very nice inside and the food looked incredible!

name: Carrie T
snippet: Nothing to do with this location- no matter the Keg the steak is always just okay which is sad given it's a steakhouse :/ This location makes a great martini though so that earned it a star:)

name: Daniel Bocanegra
snippet: One of the best steaks in the city

name: Steve Hansen
snippet: Always a pleasure to go here. Great staff, and great meal! always recommend this place to friends.

name: Frank Hemmelder
snippet: You go to the keg when you want something predictable. The food is predictable, the layout is predictable, the staff is predictable, the prices are predictable. Nothing ever changes at the Keg. Which is fine, as that is why I go there.

name: Jenna B
snippet: My favourite place for steak

name: Mel Santos
snippet: Food was good , service was excellent. Very nice interior we sat in the lounge area atmosphere was great

name: Ashleigh Ryan
snippet: The staff was amazing & quite nice. Unfortunately the food wasn't. Tough meat & not as tasty as it usually is at a Keg.

name: Josh Measures
snippet: Great service. One of the best Keg meals I have had in a long time.

name: Leo Monaco
snippet: Trendy looking bar section that fits with the style of the area. Good spot to catch a drink or dine in. The food is good, like you would expect at any Keg chain restaurant.

name: Rana Mikhael
snippet: Delicious food, beautiful ambiance and excellent customer service

name: TG Va
snippet: I wasn’t having the best experience today, so I informed the manager about it and she made it up to me big time.I wasn’t gonna be back but now I’d definitely give it another try.

name: Rocky L
snippet: Always consistently great service and food. Very attentive to allergies. My go to place when in the area....

name: Jenny KIM
snippet: I was here for celebrate my birthday. Foods were nice, staffs were also nice. I will re-visit here soon!

name: Zhuan Wang
snippet: My favourite Keg in the city. Great service every time.

name: Enrique Solórzano Toledo
snippet: Delicious food, great drinks and dessert. The service was awesome as well. Top-notch

name: D Stan
snippet: Steak perfectly done. Paired with a wine. Best in the city!

name: Tristan Alexander
snippet: Excellent playing, service, and staff

name: Lisa YEG
snippet: Consistent service. I always get a good steak, though the wait for a table on the weekends are a bit too long.

name: Cyrus Mir
snippet: Decent steaks at decent prices. Burger doesn't taste that great. Get the baked potato but NOT the double baked

name: TK Hogg
snippet: Love. Love. Love. You'll never be disappointed except if you want fun on Halloween. Was dead in there last Halloween (2015) amid a busy street scene of partiers!

name: Brendan Bane
snippet: Expensive place but the food, service and environment are top notch! If you are looking to go out for a special occasion and can afford about $75 a person the Keg would be a good choice.

name: MAISY D
snippet: great ambience and amazing steak here always!

name: Derek Anderson
snippet: Underrated. Very good food. Excellent service. Reasonable prices. Ask for Angie.

name: Boris Babich
snippet: This place is just your typical Keg, if you've been to one you've been to them all. Nothing exceptional in terms of food or service.

name: Eru Pendragon

name: Deanna Gallant
snippet: Genuinely can’t remember our severs name (bad with names) but it was just so lovely having him as our server. My boyfriend and I had come in tonight after being ignored at Oretta and leaving without even being served - we were just fuming about the situation we were just in. Our server really changed our night for the better and we really wanted to thank him for just being so pleasant and thoughtful!! If I remember his name I’ll definitely edit my review to add it! Oh and the food was delicious as always!! Much happier we ended up here as it never disappoints.
